                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030216-20-defend122 t18030216-20-punish115"></join>
               Death
            </rs>, aged 23.</p>
               <p>Recommended by the Jury on account of his good character and youth.</p>
               <p>London Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
